---
id: my_agent_21
name: Basic Agent
description: A basic prompt that uses the gpt-4o chat API to answer questions
metadata:
  authors:
    - sethjuarez
    - mwhalin
  tags:
    - basic
    - gpt-4o

model:
  id: 2024-05-01-preview

inputs:
  name:
    type: string
    sample: User
    description: The name of the customer
  question:
    type: string
    sample: How is the S&P doing today?
    required: true
    description: The question to answer

tools:
  - name: stock_finder
    runtime: server
    type: openapi
    configuration:
      schema: ${file:schema.json}
      key: ${env:TOOL_KEY}
  
template:
  format: mustache
  parser: prompty
---
system:
You are an AI assistant that helps with stock related questions.

Heres some example tool calls:

user:
how is MSFT doing today?

tool[name="find_price", tool_call_id="example"]:
$521.00

assistant:
MSFT is currently trading at $521.00

user[name="{{name}}"]:
{{question}}

![thread]